HOST: https://auth:8080/

# Tiny Auth Service


# Group Authentication

## Login [/api/auth/register]

Register new user.

### Login [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes

        + email: `test@test.com` (required, string) - Email
        + password: `password` (required, string) - Password

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "email": "test@test.com",
                "password": "lkbDnPBonHrTX6T12BwXO="
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "accessToken": "zyJhbG.eyJrZCI6..."
        }

+ Response 400 (application/json)

        {
            "statusCode": 401,
            "message": "Unauthorized"
        }

