## Validate [/api/auth/validate]

Validate JWT.

### Validate [POST]

+ Request (application/json)

    + Attributes

        + accessToken: `zyJhbG.eyJrZCI6...` (required, string) - JWT body

    + Headers

            Accept: application/json

    + Body

            {
                "accessToken": "zyJhbG.eyJrZCI6..."
            }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "statusCode": 200,
            "decodedToken": {
                "uid": 10,
                "exp": 1549130000
            }
        }

+ Response 401 (application/json)

        {
            "statusCode": 401,
            "message": "Unauthorized"
        }
